+### Chapter 17: Possibility 3 — The Deep Version, Fully Expanded
+
+*This chapter is the one the evidence most strongly supports, and the one that requires the most care to state honestly. I want to develop it fully — not as speculation, but as the best available account of what the historical pattern, combined with the specific features of the Unitary Manifold, actually implies.*
+
+**17.1 The Structure Is Not a Human Invention**
+
